div.p:
4. To Husbands.] Let the Wife see [
                     〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                  ] that she fear her Husband, Eph. 5.33. Qu. How is that to be? Answ. By being good and obedient to their own proper Husbands, (Tit. 2.5. Ephes. 5.22, 24.) in every thing. Qu. How in every thing? Ans. in every good thing as unto the Lord, Eph. 5.22. in the fear of God, Col. 3.18. as it is fit, in the Lord.—
